  "title": "Looking for Growth, Not Just a Job?",
  "description": "<p>🚨 Fresh Grads, ORD Warriors, and Adventurous Career Switchers — welcome!<br />If you’re searching for a job that’s fun, social, and filled with self-growth, our Sales & Marketing position is the perfect fit.<br /><br />We’re an <strong>international outsourced sales and marketing company</strong>, working with brands across multiple industries to drive growth through high-impact, people-focused campaigns.<br /><br />Experience? <strong>Optional</strong>. We’ll equip you with all the <em>skills </em>and <em>confidence </em>you need.<br /><br />⚡ <strong>What You’ll Experience</strong><br />🎤 High-energy events & roadshows<br />🤝 Hands-on B2B communication practice<br />😄 Face-to-face interactions that boost your people skills<br />🔥 A fun-loving, energetic team<br />🎓 Regular workshops to grow your confidence, leadership, and communication<br /><br />💰 <strong>What You’ll Get</strong><br />💵 Weekly pay + uncapped commissions<br />🏆 Recognition and bonuses for top performers<br />🚀 Opportunities to step into leadership roles<br />✈️ Local and overseas travel for learning & exposure<br />🤗 A team environment where everyone genuinely supports each other<br /><br />🚀 Looking for a job that’s meaningful, fun, and full of growth?<br />Apply now — positions are limited!</p>",
